cs.DB, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.CY, cs.DS 

The paper focuses on integrating differentially private machine learning algorithms into an RDBMS system, which involves both database management (cs.DB) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses privacy concerns (cs.CR) and provides experimental results (cs.CY) to demonstrate the effectiveness of their proposed approach. Additionally, the paper involves data analysis (cs.DS) as it deals with extracting patterns from data using machine learning.
